L2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Do not ground the switching circuit to the main ground if using a non-isolated footswitch jack! We are switching the high side, so positive voltage will already be grounded through the sleeve.<br>
